data.description: **NO REAR NEIGHBORS, FULLY FURNISHED with GOLF CART!** Discover tranquility in the resident owned 55+ gated community of Lake Henry Estates with this adorable two-bedroom, two-bath haven with extra garage storage space!  This home features a new roof (8/2023), stainless steel appliances, eat-in kitchen, an open-concept living space and abundant natural light. The residence features a welcoming primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom, a versatile second bedroom, and a private patio overlooking lush landscapes. The lakeside community offers a 9-hole golf course, swimming, boating, tennis, pickleball, and a variety of activities, making it a haven for an active lifestyle. Conveniently located near Publix, Winn-Dixie, and Walmart, along with shopping and dining options, this worry-free retreat is the hidden jewel of Polk County. Experience the serene yet vibrant lifestyle at Lake Henry Estates – visit us today!
